Line1.D5166: At bloody last, a bit of good news. Tamiyyah is a dear friend... and a hell of a cook.
Line5.D5166: They shouldn't have needed your help. Should've had Iron Wolves watching the roads, keeping them safe.
Line7.D5166: Thank you, friend... for your assistance.
VoiceDir1.D5166: Drop of relief in an ocean of worry. Warm feelings for Tamiyyah.
